data.description: Welcome to your dream home at 32141 Weatherly Cove in Spanish Fort, AL! Nestled in the sought-after, custom built home, Cambron neighborhood, this stunning residence offers the perfect blend of modern luxury and Southern charm. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting atmosphere, thanks to the expansive open floor plan that seamlessly connects the kitchen, eat-in breakfast area, and living room. The separate dining room adds a touch of elegance while maintaining the home's airy feel. The heart of this home is undoubtedly the gourmet kitchen, featuring granite countertops, a spacious island, soft-close drawers, and a walk-in pantry. Whether you're cooking for family gatherings or hosting dinner parties, this kitchen is sure to impress. With 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms, including a luxurious owner's suite, there's plenty of space for everyone. The owners bedroom boasts ample room, while the bathroom is a spa-like retreat with a huge walk-in shower, soaking tub, and the largest his and hers closets you've ever seen. Outside, you'll find yourself on a serene 1+acre lot, offering both privacy and room to roam. Enjoy the tranquility of the private backyard, perfect for relaxing or entertaining guests. And with the home situated on a quiet cul-de-sac road,  experience peaceful living at its finest. The abundance of storage space, large crown molding, and high ceilings throughout the home add to its appeal. Plus, there's a versatile flex space that can be used as an office, playroom, exercise room, homeschool room, or whatever your heart desires. Conveniently located near schools, shopping, and the I-10 interstate, commuting to Mobile or Pensacola is a breeze. Whether you're starting a family or looking for your forever home, 32141 Weatherly Cove is ready to welcome you with open arms. Come experience the best of Southern living in Spanish Fort!
